com.yantra.yfc.rcp

Interface IYRCClientUpdater


  • public interface IYRCClientUpdater
    A Plugin implemneting extension point com.yantra.yfc.rcp.YRCAutoUpdateExtn need to implement this class.

    Implementaion of this class can control behavior of the application for client auto update

    • Method Detail

      • downloadingUpdate

        int downloadingUpdate(YRCUpdateObj updateobj)
        This method will be called after "Update Check" and before "Downloading Update". the method can return one of the following
        1. DO_NOT_UPDATE: To skip update
        2. BLOCK_UI: To download update without workbench
        3. CONTINUE: To download update with workbench (DEFAULT)
        Parameters:
        updateobj -
        Returns:

      • downloadComplete

        int downloadComplete(YRCUpdateObj updateobj)
        This method will be called after "Downloading Update". the method can return one of the following
        1. INSTALL_EXIT: To install update and Close Application
        2. INSTALL_RESTART: To install update and restart Application
        3. CONTINUE: To show "Update Downloaded" dialog and install update when user restart application (DEFAULT)
        Parameters:
        updateobj -
        Returns:
